    "description": "Tiny House Simulator Demo让你亲身体验迷你住宅的建造和创造。通过打造完美的迷你房屋以满足客户的特定需求，完成客户任务，并在拍卖任务中测试你的技能，战略性建筑能够带来丰厚回报。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/title-features-zh-CN.png?t=1732892572\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.poster.avif?t=1732892572\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.webm?t=1732892572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>为客户创建迷你房屋：设计独特而温馨的轮式迷你住宅。根据客户的偏好个性化每个家居，并加入你的个人风格。无论你是打造迷人的小木屋还是优雅的极简住宅，可能性都是无限的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/title-explore-zh-CN.png?t=1732892572\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.poster.avif?t=1732892572\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.webm?t=1732892572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在一个充满活力和多样性的岛屿上展开冒险，那里每个转角都有新的惊喜。探索位于西海岸的繁华小镇，在宁静的中央湖旁放松，或向东南的山区探险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/title-freedom-zh-CN.png?t=1732892572\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/freedom.gif?t=1732892572\" /></span><br>掌控你的商业发展，设计你的迷你住宅，探索Tiny Island。开放世界的游戏玩法提供无尽的体验，可根据你的个人风格定制。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/title-tow-zh-CN.png?t=1732892572\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.poster.avif?t=1732892572\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.webm?t=1732892572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>将你的创作连接到可靠的车辆，并将它们送到岛上的满意客户那里。在蜿蜒的道路、风景如画的小路和具有挑战性的地形中穿行，以满足你的截止日期。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/title-business-zh-CN.png?t=1732892572\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.poster.avif?t=1732892572\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.webm?t=1732892572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>管理和扩展你的迷你房屋业务。投资你辛苦赚来的钱来升级你的工作坊，购买更好的车辆，或者在当地赌场试试运气。目标是建造更大更吸引人的住宅！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/title-scenery-zh-CN.png?t=1732892572\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.poster.avif?t=1732892572\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233620/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.webm?t=1732892572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>享受壮丽的景色和景点，包括游乐场、山上的风车和小岛上的灯塔。在沙滩上放松，或者探索位于西南部的繁华机场。<br><br>你准备好接受终极迷你房屋挑战了吗？开始这段激动人心的冒险，把你的微小梦想变成繁荣的事业！<br>今天就在Steam上获取Tiny House Simulator，开始打造你的梦想家园！",
